'''Ibrahim Okash''' (born 18 September 1964) is a former [[athlete]] who competed internationally for [[Somalia]]. He competed at the [[1984 Summer Olympics]] and the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].
At the 1984 Games he competed in the [[Athletics at the 1984 Summer Olympics – Men's 400 metres|400 metres]] and finished 7th in his heat and did not advance any further. At the 1988 Games he finished 8th in the [[Athletics at the 1988 Summer Olympics – Men's 800 metres|800 metres]] semi-finals.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ok/ibrahim-okash-1.html Sports Reference profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621170952/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ok/ibrahim-okash-1.html |date=2015-06-21 }}</ref>
