'''Sayidat Al-Ansar''' ([[Arabic]]:سيدات الانصار) is the women's team of the Lebanese [[association football]] club [[Al-Ansar (Lebanon)|Al-Ansar]]. ''Sayidat'' is [[Arabic]] for ''Ladies''.

